window.__KB.push({"t": "MEDICAL INSURANCE – HOSPITALIZATION & SURGICAL CLAIM FORM 醫療保險 – 住院及手術賠償表 This f", "f": "C13.pdf", "s": "MEDICAL INSURANCE – HOSPITALIZATION & SURGICAL CLAIM FORM 醫療保險 – 住院及手術賠償表 This form is applicable to both inpatient and outpatient surgical claim 本表格適用於住院或門診手術賠償 Branch code 分行編號 Advisor code 保險顧問編號 Advisor’s name 保險顧問姓名 Advisor’s Contact no. 保險顧問聯絡電話 Location 地點 PART I – TO BE COMPLETED BY THE INSURED / POLICYOWNER 第一部份 – 由受保人 / 保單持有人填寫 Important Notes 重要事項: 1. For document requirements of this claim, please refer to the Hospital Claims Instructions or scan the QR code. 有關此索償的所需文件，請參考「住院索償指引」或掃描二維碼。 2. Please read the Notice to Customers relating to the Personal Data (Privacy) Ordinance ( “Notice” ) before you complete this form. The Notice is available on Manulife’s website (www.manulife.com.hk) or upon request from your Manulife Advisor. By completing and returning to Manulife the form, you are agreeing to the Notice. 當閣下填寫此表格前，請閱畢《有關〈個人資料（私隱）條例〉的客戶通知》（「通知」）。該通知可於宏利網址 (www.manulife.com.hk) 或向閣下的宏利顧問索取。透過填妥及交 回此表格，即表示閣下同意該通知之內容。 Policy No./ Cert No. in Claim Sequence: 按索償次序的保單編號/受保證書編號: Type of products 產品類別： Name of Policyowner / Employee / Member 保單持有人 / 僱員 / 成員姓名︰ 1. Individual 個人  Group 團體  2. Individual 個人  Group 團體  Under ManuEnrich Medical Top-up Plan (“ManuEnrich”), all eligible medical expenses must first be claimed under any other available insurance coverage of the insured before claiming under ManuEnrich. If the insured is entitled to any benefits payable for such eligible medical expenses under another insurance policy issued by Manulife (either a group medical scheme or an individual medical scheme), this claim will automatically be processed & settled under such other insurance policy first and the balance will then be claimed under ManuEnrich. 根據倍康醫療加保計劃(「倍康」)，所有合資格醫療費用必須先向受保人其他可用的保險保障索償，然後才可於倍康提出索償。若受保人有權於宏利發出的其他保單下，就合資格 醫療費用獲得支付賠償（不論團體醫療計劃或個人醫療計劃），此索償個案將先自動於該其他保單進行處理及索償，餘額再於倍康進行索償。 Benefits to Claim 索償類別  Medical Reimbursement 醫療費用  Hospital Income/Special Bonus 住院現金/特別獎賞  ICU Benefit 深切治療保障 Name of Insured 受保人姓名︰ Occupation 職業︰ HKID / Passport No. 香港身份證 / 護照號碼︰ (please attach copy 請附上副本) Date of Birth 出生日期︰ (DD日/MM月/YY年) Sex 性別︰ M 男  F 女 (1) If the medical expenses are incurred outside Hong Kong or Macau, please provide the reason. 若醫療費用於香港或澳門以外地區產生，請提供原因。 (2) Please provide the reference no. of Preliminary Assessment (if applicable) 請提供初步評估之參考編號（如適用）： IFP - PA (3) Did you submit this insurance claims to other insurance company? 閣下有否於其他保險公司遞交是次保險賠償?  No 否  Yes 有  Medical reimbursement 醫療費用  Hospital income 住院現金  Others 其他 Name of Insurance Company 保險公司名稱︰ Policy No. 保單編號︰ Is / Are the submitted claim application document(s) DIGITAL receipt(s)? 閣下提交的索償申請文件是否為電子收據 ?  No 否  Yes 是 Please refer to Point 3 under Declaration and Authorization 請細閱聲明及授權的第3點  Original receipt will not be returned. Please “✓” this box for obtaining certified true copy of receipt. 正本收據將不獲發還。如需取得收據的核實副本，請於方格內加上“✓”。 (4) Have you had any prior treatment for this or related condition(s)? 閣下是否曾經因同一病況而接受治療？  No 否  Yes 是 Doctor’s Name 醫生姓名︰ Address 地址︰ Treatment Date 診治日期︰(DD日/MM月/YY年) (5) Was the hospitalization / surgery a result of an accident? 是次住院 / 手術是否由於一宗意外引致？  No 否  Yes 是 Date 日期︰ (DD日/MM月/YY年) Time 時間︰ Place 地點︰ Brief Description 經過︰  Claim emergency outpatient benefit 索償緊急門診保障  Claim the outstanding balance under the accident coverage provided by Manulife, if applicable. (Please provide the relevant policy no. above. No completion of additional \"Claim Form for Accident\"(C12) is required.) 索償餘額於宏利提供之意外保障索償，如適用。（請於上方提供相關保單編號，並無需額外填寫「意外索償表格」（C12）） Other Information / Special Request 其他資料 / 特別指示 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C13 (11/2025) 1 of 4 ePayout allows you to get money faster and have it transferred to your bank account directly without hassle. 電子支付將款項直接轉入您的銀行帳戶，令您更快收取款項，化繁為簡。 Payment Instructions (Only applicable to Individual Products) 付款指示（只適用於個人產品）: Notes 註: • e-Payout is only applicable to policyowner’s bank account, except joint account 電子支付只適用於保單持有人之銀行帳戶，不包括聯名戶口 • Default e-Payout Method will be applied (if any) if no option is specified or the specified option is invalid 如未有指明或所選擇的付款方法無法被使用，預設電子 提取付款方法（如有）將採用為是次付款方法 By e-Payout 電子支付： n a. Default e-Payout Method (i.e. last channel for receiving claims payment or policy payment through FPS/Direct Credit. If this option is selected without prior default arrangement, we will pay according to option b(i) below (if applicable). Otherwise, cheque will be issued.) 預設電子提取付款方法（即上一次經轉數快或 直接存入銀行帳戶以收取理賠金額或保單款項之渠道。如選擇此選項但未有預先設立提取安排，將根據下列 b(i) 選項處理付款（如適用），否則將以支票形式支付 OR below specified e-Payout Method (will be set as default arrangement): 或以下指定電子提取付款方法（將被設置為預設付款方式）： n b. Direct Credit to one of my following bank accounts (up to HKD300,000/USD37,500) 直接存入本人下列其中一個銀行帳戶（限額港元 300,000／美元37,500） n (i) Current autopay bank account in HKD currency for payment of premium and levy 現時繳付保費及徵費之港元自動轉帳銀行帳戶 n (ii) Bank account specified below 以下指定的銀行帳戶： 1. Name of account holder 帳戶持有人姓名 : 2. Currency and Bank Name 貨幣及銀行名稱 n HKD Bank Account 港元銀行帳戶 Bank Name 銀行名稱 : n USD Bank Account (only applicable for USD Policy) 美元銀行帳戶（只適用於美元保單） Bank Name 銀行名稱 : THE HONGKONG AND SHANGHAI BANKING CORPORATION LTD 香港上海滙豐銀行有限公司 3. Bank No. 銀行編號 Branch No. Bank Account No. 分行編號 銀行帳戶號碼 Please provide account proof (e.g. bank statement or bank book copy showing the name of account holder and account number) 請提供帳戶資料證明（如列有帳戶持有人之姓名及帳戶號碼之銀行帳單或銀行存摺影印本） n c. FPS to my default receiving account (in HKD only, up to HKD1,000,000) 轉數快至本人預設的收款帳戶（只限港元，限額港元1,000,000） Hong Kong Mobile Phone Number 香港手提電話號碼 : (852) Others, Country / Region Code & Mobile Phone Number 其他，國家/區域號碼及手提電話號碼 :( ) Remarks 備註: - The above specified Faster Payment System (FPS) mobile phone number is for FPS payment only and will not be updated to your contact information in our record. 上述指定之手提電話號碼只用於轉數快轉賬，並不會用作更新您於我們紀錄內的聯絡資料。 - For payout through FPS, only applicable to payment with maximum daily transaction limit not exceeding HKD1,000,000 (or equivalent) per policy. If payment is e"});
window.__KB.push({"t": "CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE PROGRESSIVE MUSCULAR ATROPHY 重病保障索償表格 － 進行性肌肉萎縮 Pol", "f": "C20.pdf", "s": "CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE PROGRESSIVE MUSCULAR ATROPHY 重病保障索償表格 － 進行性肌肉萎縮 Policy No. 保單編號： PART II – This Attending Physician’s Statement must be completed by a qualified and registered physician at the insured’s expense 第二部份 – 本應診醫生報告必須由受保人自費聘請之合資格註冊醫生填寫 1. Name of Patient 病人姓名 2. I.D. Card No. 身份證號碼 3. Age 年齡 4. Are you the patient's usual medical attendant? 閣下是否病人之私人醫生？ No 否 Yes 是 If \"Yes\", give details 若「是」，請填寫有關資料。 Period of Consultation Past Health History 應診期間 病人過往健康情況 5. a) Date on which you first attended the patient for this disease (Progressive Muscular Atrophy). 首次為病人診治是項病症（進行性肌肉萎縮）之日期。 b) What was the symptom(s) experienced prior to the first consultation? And for how long? 病人首次求診前有何症狀？該等症狀已存在多久？ c) When was the patient informed of the diagnosis? (Please give exact date) 何時通知病人診斷結果？（請填寫準確日期） 6. Give full and exact details of the diagnosis. 請詳盡填寫確實診斷資料。 7. Had the patient any past history of the disease specified above or related illness? 病人過往曾否患有上述疾病或有關疾病？ No 否 Yes 有 If \"Yes\", give details 若「有」，請填寫有關資料。 Name of Attended Physician(s) Date of Consultation Address(es) Exact Diagnosis 應診醫生姓名 診治日期 地址 確實診斷資料 8. Is there anything in the patient's family history which would have increased the risk of Progressive Muscular Atrophy? 病人之家庭背景有否任何增加病人患上進行性肌肉萎縮機會之事項？ 9. Please give details of the patient's habits in relation to alcohol, drugs and smoking. 請填寫病人飲酒、吸毒或吸煙習慣之詳情。 10. Please describe the underlying cause of Progressive Muscular Atrophy. 請指出導致進行性肌肉萎縮之原因。 11. Was the disease diagnosed by a consultant neurologist? If so, please provide us with the name and address of neurologist. 病人是否經神經科顧問醫生診斷患有該疾病？如是，請提供該醫生的姓名及地址。 12. Is there any evidence of wasting of muscles and/or increased spasticity? 病人有否出現肌肉萎縮及／或痙攣加劇？ 13. Please give details of radiological investigations, M.R.I., C T scan, laboratory evidence and any other test results for reference. 請提供放射檢驗、磁力共振、電腦斷層掃描、實驗室證據或其他檢驗結果的詳情以供參考。 14. Please provide details of physicians to whom the patient has been referred or attended for this disease. 請提供曾為病人診治是項病症之醫生資料。 (We would be grateful for copies of any relevant medical report that are available ) （敬請提供任何有關醫療報告副本） Name of Physician(s) and/or Hospital(s) Address(es) Date of Consultation(s) and/or Period of Confinement(s) 醫生姓名及／或醫院名稱 地址 診治及／或留院日期 15. If there is any further information which, in your opinion, will assist us in assessing this claim, please furnish such information below. 閣下認為有否其他資料可協助本公司審核是項索償申請？請提供有關資料。 5 Signature 簽署 Date 日期 Qualification 資格 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C20 (11/2025) Name of Physician (with stamp) 醫生姓名（連印章） Address 地址 Tel. No. 電話號碼 1 of 1"});
window.__KB.push({"t": "CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE BENIGN BRAIN TUMOUR Policy No. 保單編號： 重病保障索償表格 － 良性腦", "f": "C26.pdf", "s": "CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE BENIGN BRAIN TUMOUR Policy No. 保單編號： 重病保障索償表格 － 良性腦腫瘤 PART II – This Attending Physician’s Statement must be completed by a qualified and registered physician at the insured’s expense 第二部份 – 本應診醫生報告必須由受保人自費聘請之合資格註冊醫生填寫 1. Name of Patient 病人姓名 2. I.D. Card No. 身份證號碼 3. Age 年齡 4. Are you the patient's usual medical attendant? 閣下是否病人之私人醫生？ No 否 Yes 是 If \"Yes\", give details 若「是」，請填寫有關資料。 Period of Consultation Past Health History 應診期間 病人過往健康情況 5. a) Date on which you first attended the patient for this disease (Benign Brain Tumour). 首次為病人診治是項病症（良性腦腫瘤）之日期。 b) What was the symptom(s) experienced prior to the first consultation? And for how long? 病人首次求診前有何症狀？該等症狀已存在多久？ c) When was the patient informed of the diagnosis? (Please give exact date) 何時通知病人診斷結果？（請填寫準確日期） 6. Give full and exact details of the diagnosis. 請詳盡填寫確實診斷資料。 7. Had the patient any past history of the disease specified above or related illness? 病人過往曾否患有上述疾病或有關疾病？ No 否 Yes 有 If \"Yes\", give details 若「有」，請填寫有關資料。 Name of Attended Physician(s) Date of Consultation Address(es) Exact Diagnosis 應診醫生姓名 診治日期 地址 確實診斷資料 8. Is there anything in the patient's family history which would have increased the risk of Benign Brain Tumour? 病人之家庭背景有否任何增加病人患上良性腦腫瘤機會之事項？ 9. Please give details of the patient's habits in relation to alcohol, drugs and smoking. 請填寫病人飲酒、吸毒或吸煙習慣之詳情。 10. Please describe the underlying cause of Benign Brain Tumour. 請指出導致良性腦腫瘤之原因。 11. Was the disease diagnosed by a consultant neurologist? If so, please provide us with the name and address of neurologist. 病人是否經神經科顧問醫生診斷患有該疾病？如是，請提供該醫生的姓名及地址。 12. Please give details of the severity of the illness with respect to the followings: 請就以下方面描述病人的病情： a) Is the tumour benign? What was the histology of the tumour? 病人的腫瘤是否屬良性？請說明腫瘤的組織。 b) Which part of the brain was involved? Was it completely localized? If not, was the pituitary gland or spine also involved? 腫瘤涉及腦部哪個部位？是否已完全 局限化？如否，是否涉及腦下垂體或腦脊椎？ c) Is the tumour in the form of cysts, granulomas, haematomas, other malformations in the arteries or veins of the brain? 病人的腫瘤是否屬水囊腫、肉芽瘤、血腫， 或腦動脈或靜脈畸形？ d) Was there any surgical removal performed? If yes, please provide the surgery name and date. 是否進行過手術切除？如是，請提供手術名稱和日期。 e) Please comment on any significant neurological functional impairment caused by the tumour? If yes, how long has it lasted and is it permanent in nature? 請評論腫瘤是否造成了任何顯著的神經系統功能受損？如是，持續了多久？是永久性的嗎？ 13. Please give details of radiological investigations, M.R.I., C T scan, laboratory evidence and any other test results for reference. 請提供放射檢驗、磁力共振、電腦斷層掃描、實驗室證據或其他檢驗結果的詳情以供參考。 14. Please provide details of physicians to whom the patient has been referred or attended for this disease. 請提供曾為病人診治是項病症之醫生資料。 (We would be grateful for copies of any relevant medical report that are available ) （敬請提供任何有關醫療報告副本） Name of Physician(s) and/or Hospital(s) Address(es) Date of Consultation(s) and/or Period of Confinement(s) 醫生姓名及／或醫院名稱 地址 診治及／或留院日期 15. If there is any further information which, in your opinion, will assist us in assessing this claim, please furnish such information below. 閣下認為有否其他資料可協助本公司審核是項索償申請？請提供有關資料。 5 Signature 簽署 Date 日期 Qualification 資格 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C26 (11/2025) Name of Physician (with stamp) 醫生姓名（連印章） Address 地址 Tel. No. 電話號碼 1 of 1"});
window.__KB.push({"t": "CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE COMA / LESS SEVERE COMA 重病保障索償表格 － 昏迷／次級嚴重昏迷 Policy", "f": "C32.pdf", "s": "CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE COMA / LESS SEVERE COMA 重病保障索償表格 － 昏迷／次級嚴重昏迷 Policy No. 保單編號： PART II – This Attending Physician’s Statement must be completed by a qualified and registered physician at the insured’s expense 第二部份 – 本應診醫生報告必須由受保人自費聘請之合資格註冊醫生填寫 1. Name of Patient 病人姓名 2. I.D. Card No. 身份證號碼 3. Age 年齡 4. Are you the patient's usual medical attendant? 閣下是否病人之私人醫生？ No 否 Yes 是 If \"Yes\", give details 若「是」，請填寫有關資料。 Period of Consultation Past Health History 應診期間 病人過往健康情況 5. a) Date on which the patient first consulted you related to the condition (Coma/Less Severe Coma). 病人就是項疾病（昏迷/次級嚴重昏迷）首次向閣下求診的 日期（DD日/ MM月/YY年）。 b) What were the symptoms? 病人之病徵？ c) How long had the patient been experiencing these symptoms before the first consultation? 病人在首次求診前已患有此病徵多久？ d) When was the patient informed of the diagnosis? (Please give exact date) 何時通知病人診斷結果?（請填寫準確日期） 6. Give full and exact details of the diagnosis. 請詳盡填寫確實診斷資料。 7. Had the patient any past history of the disease specified above or related illness? 病人過往曾否患有上述疾病或有關疾病？ No 否 Yes 有 If \"Yes\", give details 若「有」，請填寫有關資料。 Name of Attended Physician(s) Date of Consultation Address(es) Exact Diagnosis 應診醫生姓名 診治日期 地址 確實診斷資料 8. Is there anything in the patient’s family history which would have increased the risk of the disease specified above? 病人之家庭背景有否任何增加病人患上上述疾病機 會之事項？ 9. Please give details of the patient's habits in relation to alcohol, drugs and smoking. 請填寫病人飲酒、吸毒或吸煙習慣之詳情。 10. Please describe the extent of the coma. 請描述昏迷之狀況。 i. Date of onset. 病發日期： ( / / ) DD日/MM月/YY年 ii. Is there any reaction or response to external stimuli? 對外來刺激有沒有反應？ Yes 有 No 沒有 If no response, how long has it persisted? 如沒有反應，持續了多久？ iii. Is there any reaction or response to internal needs? 對體內需求有沒有反應？ Yes 有 No 沒有 If no response, how long has it persisted? 如沒有反應，持續了多久？ iv. Does the Insured persistently require the use of a life support system which requires the use of a respirator for a period of time? 受保人有否於某一段時間內須持續 利用生命維持系統（包括呼吸器）維持生命？ Yes 有 No 沒有 If yes, how long has it persisted? 如有，持續了多久？ v. Is there any permanent neurological defect? 有沒有永久性的神經機能缺損？ Yes 有 No 沒有 If yes, please give details. 如有，請詳述？ vi. How long is it expected that the Insured will remain in coma? 請估計受保人之昏迷狀態會維持多久？ vii. Was the coma confirmed by a neurologist or neurosurgeon? 是否經腦神經專科或神經外科註冊醫生確診？ Yes 是 No 否 Please give Name and Address of the neurologist or neurosurgeon confirming the diagnosis if it is not the undersigned. 若非由填寫此表格之醫生確診，請提供確診 之腦神經專科或神經外科註冊醫生之姓名及地址。 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C32 (11/2025) 1 of 2 Policy No. 保單編號： 11. i. What was the cause of the coma? 昏迷是因何引致？ ii. Was the coma medically induced? 是否醫療誘導的昏迷？ Yes 是 No 否 iii. Was the coma directly resulted from alcohol or drug abuse? 是否直接因酒精或濫用藥物引致？ Yes 是 No 否 iv. Was there any known underlying causes or precipitating illness leading to the coma? If so, please state any treatment history. 有沒有已知的原因或潛在的疾病引致 昏迷發生? 如有, 請列出過往之治療記錄。 Yes 有 No 沒有 Treatment History 過往之治療記錄： 12. Please provide details of physicians to whom the patient has been referred or attended for this disease. 請提供曾為病人診治是項病症之醫生資料。 (We would be grateful for copies of any relevant medical report that are available ) （敬請提供任何有關醫療報告副本） Name of Physician(s) and/or Hospital(s) Address(es) Date of Consultation(s) and/or Period of Confinement(s) 醫生姓名及／或醫院名稱 地址 診治及／或留院日期 13. If there is any further information which, in your opinion, will assist us in assessing this claim, please furnish such information below. 閣下認為有否其他資料可協助本公司審核是項索償申請？請提供有關資料。 5 Signature 簽署 Date 日期 Qualification 資格 Name of Physician (with stamp) 醫生姓名（連印章） Address 地址 Tel. No. 電話號碼 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C32 (11/2025) 2 of 2"});
