window.__KB.push({"t": "This is a fillable form. You can fill it in and print it for signature. Print Re", "f": "T40.pdf", "s": "This is a fillable form. You can fill it in and print it for signature. Print Reset Save APPLICATION FOR CHANGE OF LIFE INSURED 更改受保人申請表 Branch code 分行編號 Location 地點 Advisor’s Code 保險顧問編號 Advisor’s Name 保險顧問姓名 Advisor’s Contact no. 保險顧問聯絡電話 Policy no. 保單編號 Full name of Policyowner 保單持有人姓名 Full name of Current Life Insured 現受保人姓名 Points to Note 申請須知： • This Application for Change of Life Insured form ('Form') is used for change of Life Insured under the policy with Change of Life Insured Provision. 此更改受保人申請表（「申請表」）於附有更改受保人條款之保單用作更改受保人。 • Please provide the full name as shown on Identity Card or Passport or Business Registration Certificate or other relevant Identity Document. 請提供身份證或護照或商業登記證或其他有關身份證明文件所示之全名。 • Please complete this Form in English BLOCK letters legibly with Policyowner’s signature that corresponds with the Company record. Any amendments to this Form should be clearly indicated and countersigned by the Policyowner. 請用英文正楷清楚地填寫此表格，並由保單持有人簽署，而簽名必須與本公司檔案相符。 在此表格內如有任何更改，保單持有人必須清楚註明並在更改的位置簽署作實。 • Manulife shall have the right to revise this Form from time to time and to accept or reject the Form submitted by you if you fail to fulfill the Company’s requirements. 宏利有權隨時更改表格內容，如閣下未能符合本公司的有關規定，宏利將保留接受或拒絕閣下遞交之申請表的權利。 • In this Form, ‘Manulife’ and the ‘Company’ refer to Manulife (International) Limited. 於此申請表內，「宏利」，「本公司」及「貴公司」是指宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司。 • After your change request is processed, you will receive a digital confirmation notice/endorsement (if digital version is available) if you have opted for e-statements/e-notices under “Other statements/notices/endorsement” and respective paper notice/endorsement will not be provided. You can access your e-Notices and e-Endorsements by logging in to our website or app. 在您的申請處理完成後，如您在「其他結單／通知／批註」類別下選擇了電子結單／通知，您將收取電子版通知／批註（如電子版可供提供），而該通知／批註將不會獲發紙本。您可以 登入我們的網站或流動應用程式，查看您的電子通知及電子批註。 Important Notes for the Change of Life Insured application 更改受保人申請的重要事項： (1) “Effective Date of Change” means the effective date of change of Life Insured under the policy as recorded in the relevant Endorsement issued by the Company. 「更改生效日」指由本公司簽發的有關批註上記錄的更改保單受保人之生效日期。 (2) The Policyowner may apply for change of Life Insured under the policy starting from the first policy anniversary or one year from the policy is issued, whichever is the later. 保單持有人可於第一個保單周年日或保單簽發一年後（以較後者為準）提出更改受保人的申請。 (3) As at the Effective Date of Change, the New Life Insured must meet either one of the following conditions : 於更改生效日，新受保人必須符合以下其中一個條件： i. the actual age of the New Life Insured is 60 or below; or 新受保人的實際年齡為60歲或以下；或 ii. the actual age of the New Life Insured is not greater than that of the Current Life Insured and is not greater than 75 (only applicable for ManuGrand Saver, ManuImperial Saver or ManuCentury) or the age limit that specified in the eligible products Change of Life Insured provision if otherwise. 新受保人的實際年齡不大於現受保人的年齡及不大於75歲（只適用於豐譽傳承保障計劃、創富傳承保障計劃或世紀傳承保障計劃）或適用產品之更改受保人條款內所指定歲數之上限。 (4) If the Effective Date of Change falls on a policy anniversary date, the “Age” of the New Life Insured means the age nearest birthday as at the relevant policy anniversary date. If the Effective Date of Change does not fall on a policy anniversary date, the \"Age\" of the New Life Insured means the age nearest birthday (i) as at the Effective Date of Change for the period from the Effective Date of Change up to the end of the policy year in which the Effective Date of Change falls, and (ii) as at the relevant policy anniversary date for the next policy year onwards. Premium will be calculated based on the age nearest birthday so applied. 如更改生效日在保單週年日，新受保人的「年齡」是指相關保單周年日當天最接近一個生日所達之歲數。如更改生效日不是在保單週年日，則新受保人的「年齡」(i) 由更改生效日至更改生 效日所屬之保單年度完結期間，是指更改生效日當天最接近一個生日所達之歲數；及 (ii) 由下一保單年度開始，是指相關保單周年日當天最接近一個生日所達之歲數。保費將根據相應的 最接近一個生日所達之歲數計算。 (5) Both Current Life Insured and New Life Insured must be alive at the time of change of Life Insured. 於更改受保人生效時，現受保人及新受保人必須同時在世。 (6) The coverage on the New Life Insured shall commence on the Effective Date of Change, and the coverage on the Current Life Insured shall cease at the same time when the coverage on the New Life Insured commences. 新受保人的保障將於更改生效日開始生效，而現受保人的保障將於新受保人的保障生效的一刻同時終止。 (7) Change of Life Insured is not available to policies with irrevocable beneficiary(ies) designation. 更改受保人不適用於已指定不可撤換受益人的保單。 (8) Upon the change of Life Insured of the policy, any beneficiary designation previously made will be automatically revoked on the Effective Date of Change. 於更改保單受保人後，任何較早前所指定的受益人將於更改生效日自動被撤銷。 (9) (Only applicable to ManuGrand Saver/ManuImperial Saver) Upon the change of Life Insured of the policy, all the existing supplementary benefits (if any, with the exception of Payor Benefit provided that the following conditions are met as at the Effective Date of Change) under the policy will be automatically terminated on the Effective Date of Change. Where the following conditions are met, the premium (calculated based on the prevailing premium rate) and the coverage period of Payor Benefit (if any) may be adjusted based on the Age of the New Life Insured: （只適用於豐譽傳承保障計劃／創富傳承保障計劃）於更改保單受保人後，附加於保單上之所有附加保障（如有，除保費支付人利益附加保障於更改生效日時符合以下情況外）將由更改 生效日起自動終止。如符合以下情況，保費支付人利益附加保障（如有）之保費(根據當時的保費率計算）及保障年期將根據新受保人的年齡而可能有所調整： i. The age nearest birthday of the New Life Insured is below 16, and the New Life Insured was born for at least 15 days; and 新受保人之最接近一個生日所達之歲數為16歲以下，以及新受保人已出生不少於15日；及 ii. The difference in age (as determined based on the age nearest birthday) between the New Life Insured and the Payor under the Payor Benefit is 45 years or below. 新受保人與保費支付人利益附加保障下的保費支付人以最接近一個生日計算所達歲數差距為45年或以下。 (10) Unless otherwise mentioned under Important Notes (9) above, all the existing supplementary benefits (if any) under the policy will be automatically terminated on the Effective Date of Change and no subsequent addition of any supplementary benefits is allowed upon the change of Life Insured of the policy. 除以上重要事項(9)提及外，於更改保單受保人後，附加於保單上之所有附加保障（如有）將於更改保單受保人的生效日起自動終止，其後亦不可附加任何附加保障。 (11) The 2-ye"});
window.__KB.push({"t": "This is a fillable form. You can fill it in and print it for signature. Print Po", "f": "T50.pdf", "s": "This is a fillable form. You can fill it in and print it for signature. Print Policy No. 保單編號 Apollo Protection Linked Plan Investment Choice Services Form 傲宏保障投資相連計劃 投資選項服務申請表 Branch code 分行編號 Insurance Advisor code 保險顧問編號 Insurance Advisor's name 保險顧問姓名 Contact no. 聯絡電話 Full name of Policyowner 保單持有人姓名 Reset Save Location 地點 Important Notes 重要事項： (1) All dollar amounts are stated in US dollar unless otherwise stated. 除特別指明外，所有金額皆以美元為貨幣單位。 (2) Please ensure the correct Code is used by referring to the Investment Choice Table and read the remarks before form filling (if applicable). 請參考投資選項表以便填上正確的編號，並於填寫此表格前參閱有關部分之註釋（如適用）。 (3) Any amendments should be endorsed by the policyowner in full signature. 任何資料如有更改，保單持有人必須在更改的位置簽署作實。 (4) Manulife (International) Limited (the \"Company\" or \"Manulife\") shall have the right to update this form from time to time and to accept or reject the form submitted by you if you fail to fulfill the Company’s requirements. 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司（「本公司」或「宏利」）有權隨時更新表格內容，如閣下未能符合本公司的有關規定，本公司將保留接受或拒絕閣下遞交之申請表格的權利。 (5) Please indicate the type of investment choice service requested by putting a “  ” in the appropriate box. 請註明所要求之投資選項服務並於適當方格內填上「  」號。 (6) Allocation percentage of each investment choice selected should be in whole number. 所選每項投資選項分配百分比必須為整數。 (7) To effect the instruction, this form should be completed, signed and received by the Company by 3:00 p.m. Hong Kong time provided that the day is a business day. 如欲辦理有關指示，須填妥並簽署本表格，並於營業日內香港時間下午3時前送達本公司。 (8) Please provide the information required in this form, otherwise, the Company would not be able to comply with the relevant regulatory requirements. If you do not provide us the necessary information / forms in timely manner, the Company may not be able to process your application or may even reject your application and we will not bear any loss that may arise. 請根據此表格提供所需資料，否則，本公司將無法遵從相關規管要求。如閣下未能及時提交需要的資料／表格，本公司可能無法處理閣下的申請甚或拒絕閣下的申請，亦不會承擔任何可 能因此引致的損失。 (9) Please read the Investment Choice Brochure of Apollo Protection Linked Plan and the offering documents of the underlying funds corresponding to the investment choices to understand the nature and risks of the underlying funds. 請參閱傲宏保障投資相連計劃的投資選項手冊及投資選項的相關基金的銷售文件，以了解相關基金的性質及風險。 (10) You should select the investment choice(s) only if you understand the nature and risks of the investment choice(s) and its underlying fund(s), and have sufficient net worth to be able to assume the risks and bear the potential losses of trading in relation to the investment choices selected. 閣下在選擇投資選項前，請閣下必須了解該投資選項及相關基金的性質及風險，並需要持有足夠的淨資產承擔與所選投資選項有關的相關風險並承擔有關的潛在損失；否則，閣下不應 選擇該投資選項。 (11) You may be exposed to the additional associated risks if the selected mix of underlying investment choices you intend to allocate through top-up premiums or switch in, after policy inception, is inconsistent with your risk profile and knowledge (including investment knowledge in derivatives). 如果閣下打算在保單生效後，就增額保費所選擇分配的相關投資選項組合或轉入的相關投資選項組合，與閣下的風險承擔能力及知識（包括對衍生產品的相關投資知識）不相符，則閣下 可能需承受額外相關風險。 (12) You may be exposed to additional associated risks if you are investing in investment choice(s) of which underlying fund(s) is/are classified as derivative fund(s). The volatility of these underlying fund(s) may increase or decrease from their derivative usage, and may suffer losses. Please refer to the offering documents of the respective underlying fund(s) for details. 如閣下所選的投資選項連繫至的相關基金被歸類為衍生產品基金，閣下或因而可能需承受額外相關風險。此等相關基金的波幅或因衍生產品的使用而上升或下降，或因而出現虧損。詳 情請參閱各相關基金的銷售文件。 (13) Please contact your advisor or visit our Customer Website at www.manulife.com.hk for ascertain the latest available investment choices. 請聯絡閣下的顧問或瀏覽宏利網站 (www.manulife.com.hk) 查閱最新可供選擇的投資選項。 (14) You are advised to complete the Risk Profile Questionnaire to assess your risk profile before investing. If there are any material changes to the information in the questionnaire provided previously and / or the questionnaire provided was submitted over 12 months, please complete the Risk Profile Questionnaire to assess your risk profile again. Please visit our website or contact your licensed insurance intermediary for details of the risk level of the respective investment choice. 我們建議閣下於投資前填寫「風險承擔能力問卷」以評估閣下之風險承受程度。如閣下於較早前遞交的「風險承擔能力問卷」內所提供的資料有重大變更及/或閣下所提供的問卷已超過12 個月，我們建議閣下重新填寫該問卷以評估閣下之風險承受程度。有關各相關投資選項的風險級別詳情，請瀏覽本公司網頁或聯絡閣下的持牌保險中介人。 (15) Please read the Notice to Customers relating to the Personal Data (Privacy) Ordinance (\"Notice\") before you complete this form. The Notice is available on Manulife's website (www.manulife.com.hk) or upon request from your Manulife Advisor. By completing and returning to Manulife the form, you are agreeing to the Notice. 當閣下填寫此表格前，請閱畢《有關〈個人資料（私隱）條例〉的客戶通知》。該通知可於宏利網址 (www.manulife.com.hk) 或向閣下的宏利顧問索取。透過填妥及交回此表格，即表示閣下同 意該通知之內容。 Type of Application 申請類別 £ Change in PremiumPayment Mode 更改保費繳付形式 £ Change in Regular Premium Allocation Instruction 更改定期保費分配指示 £ Lump-Sum Top-up Premium 一筆過增額保費 (Only applicable after Premium Payment Period 只適用於保費繳付期後) £ Autopay 自動轉帳 £ Switching 轉換 £ Partial Withdrawal 提取部分款項 (Only applicable after Mandatory Contribution Period 只適用於必要供款期後) £ Full Surrender 全數退保 Please complete 請填寫 ● Part A1 第一部份 (A1) ● Part A2 & D 第一部份 (A2) 及第四部份（if applicable 如適用） ● Part A3 第一部份 (A3) ● Part B 第二部份 ● Part C & D 第三及第四部份（if applicable 如適用） ● Part E & G 第五及第七部份 ● Part F & G 第六及第七部份 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 T50 (12/2025) 1 of 8 Part A1: Change in Premium Payment Mode 第一部份A1：更改保費繳付形式 Premium Payment Mode 保費繳付形式 Policy No. 保單編號 Monthly 月繳 Annual 年繳 E ective month and year 生效月份及年份 （ MM 月 / YYYY 年 ） (If no speciﬁc instruction is given here, the eﬀective month and year will be the request processing date. 閣下於此欄並無作出特別指示，生效月份及年份將以處理申請當日為準） Part A2: Change in Regular Premium Allocation Instruction 第一部份A2：更改定期保費分配指示 Investment Choice Code (Please refer to Investment Choice Brochure / Investment Choice Table) 投資選項編號（請參閱投資選項手冊／投資選項表） Regular Premium Allocation 定期保費分配 (% 百分比) (The percentage allocated per Investment Choice"});
